OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773831918
OL,3,CBirmingham Airport flights to the UAE
OL,4,Cand Qatar cancelled across the entire
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FA number of flights between Birmingham
OL,8,FAirport, Qatar and the United Arab
OL,9,FEmirates (UAE) have been cancelled
OL,10,Ftoday (Tuesday 17 May).
OL,12,FIt comes a day after flights were
OL,13,Ftemporarily suspended at Dubai
OL,14,FInternational Airport after a fire
OL,15,Fbroke out nearby on Monday following a
OL,16,Fdrone-related incident.
OL,18,FTwo flights from Birmingham Airport to
OL,19,FDubai, UAE and one to Doha, Qatar,
OL,20,Fhave been cancelled.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
