OL,3,CBirmingham Airport flights to the UAE
OL,4,Cand Qatar cancelled across the entire
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FOne arrival flight has also been
OL,8,Fcancelled from Dubai and one from Doha.
OL,10,FHere is the full list of flights to be
OL,11,Faffected today (Tuesday 17 March):
OL,13,FBirmingham Airport told ITV News
OL,14,FCentral, "Passengers are advised to
OL,15,Fcheck the status of their flight with
OL,16,Fthe airlines.
OL,18,F"As this is an evolving situation,
OL,19,Fthey must be first port of call as
OL,20,Fdecision makers over flights."
